{"root":{"data":{"id":"djxaeurqf3c0","created":1783930014058,"text":"STM32-PW200烧录器","font-size":32},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djxbgtlyb9c0","created":1783932989370,"text":"电源电路","progress":1,"font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djxbirues540","created":1783933142256,"text":"Vin：DC5V输入电源管理芯片MP3429；Vout：DC5.2V输出","layout":null,"progress":2,"font-size":18},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djxbq2o9aq00","created":1783933714378,"text":"线性稳压芯片U1/U2，1脚分别接主控PD2/PC12，通过高低电平控制目标板断电/启动，充当开关作用","progress":3,"font-size":18},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djxbslqnm4w0","created":1783933912610,"text":"DC-DC降压HT7833，VIN 5V，VO3.3V给主控芯片供电","progress":4,"font-size":18},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djxbgwlh44o0","created":1783932995871,"text":"TYPE-C输入","progress":1,"font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djxbv2k1om00","created":1783934105944,"text":"USART，USB（DM/DP）跨接在线路上，用于防静电和热插拔","progress":2,"font-size":18},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djxbhuk3vuo0","created":1783933069799,"text":"烧录信号传输","progress":1,"font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djxcameiiq80","created":1783935324608,"text":"通过双电源供电芯片，完美匹配不同电压范围芯片","progress":2,"font-size":18},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djxchgbmwaw0","created":1783935859922,"text":"PA3/PA2--NG/OK，传输烧录成功/失败信号，并触发LED灯点亮","expandState":"expand","progress":2},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djxchn75g7s0","created":1783935874888,"text":"U15：主控PC0，TDI（JTAG测试数据输入），DIR连接PC15，负责调转数据传输方向；高电平A-B，低电平B-A","expandState":"expand","progress":2},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djxciec03ds0","created":1783935933955,"text":"U16：PB13/PB6--SWCLK/RST，对应时钟信号/复位信号，DIR连接PC5,调转数据传输方向；高电平A-B，低电平B-A","progress":2},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djxcn21uap40","created":1783936299040,"text":"U17：PC3/PC1-- BOOT/nTRST。","progress":2},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djxcpanbgeg0","created":1783936474481,"text":"PC2高电平时，拉低BOOT引脚运行固件刷写程序；nTRST为JTAG异步复位信号"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djxcq35h69s0","created":1783936536529,"text":"DIR连接PC15，高低电平调转数据传输方向"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djxcrauzc6g0","created":1783936631673,"text":"U13：按键按下，PC4检测低电平，开启离线下载","progress":2},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djxcuot09hc0","created":1783936897121,"text":"U14：PB14/PB12输入，SWDIO输出，PB15控制数据传输方向，高低电平切换","progress":2},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djxcznbon6o0","created":1783937285717,"text":"PB8/PB9--SWIM（单线接口模块）信号线，双向传输"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djxbif86ths0","created":1783933114791,"text":"LED指示","progress":1,"font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djxd2joad0w0","created":1783937512865,"text":"LED1（电源指示灯），通电即亮"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djxd30neizk0","created":1783937549817,"text":"LED2（status就绪），PC7高电平点亮"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djxbijhscvs0","created":1783933124079,"text":"蜂鸣器","progress":1,"font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djxd13nmupc0","created":1783937399633,"text":"PB5高电平，蜂鸣器发声","progress":2},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}